						<summary>

						<p>This is also damaged.</p>						

						<p>The details of the transaction are not clear, but mention is made of a gift of 50 sheep left in charge of the <hi rend="italic">sabhā</hi> of the place for burning a lamp in the temple of Tirunāgīśvaram-Uḍaiya-Mahādēvar. Reference is made to one Kuvāvaṉ Śatturugaṇḍappēraiyaṉ of Koṭṭiyūr and to a certain Poyyilippēraiyaṉ.</p>						

						</summary>
